Our Vision

To redefine Koreas AI infrastructure by building a sovereign, scalable, and globally competitive compute platform.

Rayon exists to empower nations, enterprises, and innovators with independent AI acceleration engineered for performance, resilience, and long-term technological leadership.

Platform Architecture

Strategic Market Position

The global AI data center market is entering an accelerated expansion phase, driven by large language models, edge AI deployment, and sovereign AI initiatives. However, compute supply remains highly concentrated, creating structural vulnerability for nations and enterprises dependent on external GPU ecosystems.

Rayon positions Korea to strengthen domestic AI compute capability, diversify supply chains, and secure long-term infrastructure competitiveness. It is not merely a product it is a strategic compute foundation aligned with national AI semiconductor priorities.

  • Explosive AI Infrastructure Demand Growth
  • GPU Supply Concentration Risk Mitigation
  • Strategic Semiconductor Independence
  • Domestic AI Cluster Enablement

Why Korea Optimization Matters

AI hardware deployment efficiency is fundamentally shaped by regional infrastructure realities power density limits, rack standards, cooling design, regulatory frameworks, and operational patterns. Generic global GPU designs do not always maximize local deployment efficiency.

Rayon is architected specifically for Korean infrastructure characteristics. By aligning compute density, thermal profiles, and system integration to domestic data center conditions, it enhances TCO efficiency, deployment stability, and long-term operational sustainability.

  • Rack-Level Infrastructure Alignment
  • Power Density & Grid Optimization
  • Cooling System Compatibility
  • Regulatory & Policy Synchronization
  • Localized Supply Chain Strategy
